description:
We are delighted to introduce you to this amazing opportunity in the heart of Robina. This one is not to be missed, a beautiful home set in a quiet cul de sac and located close to everything amazing Robina has to offer. This property is vacant and available for you to move in before Christmas!

Neighbouring well-kept properties, this is a perfect residence for all family variations. A strong family community and only a short drive to Robina Primary School, Robina Pavilion, Golf Course, children parks, local shops, Robina Town Centre, CBUS stadium, Bond University and all other necessary amenities.

This home overlooks and borders the planned 17-hectare "Greenheart" parklands including adventure play areas, water play, event space, bike/scooter track, and BBQ facilities to begin construction this year cementing Robina as the ultimate family suburb. This property sits within the catchment for Robina State School and Merrimac State High School, with a choice of private schools nearby.

Here, you can forget the world and enjoy all you need in your own backyard. It's massive, with beautifully coloured panoramic views. The house is also the perfect platform to renovate and has so much potential to create something incredibly special.

From the moment you enter through the double doors, you will be captivated by the open plan design of the home and the lay of the land.

This 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home offers multiple living areas, high vaulted ceiling in the spacious lounge room and a modern kitchen with stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances with views to the rear garden from every room.

This home is ready to move into today, with nothing to do. Set on a huge level block with plenty of space for the kids to play.

Do not delay your inspection!

Features:
• Private setting surrounded by parklands and waterways at the rear of the property
• Family home with multiple living areas
• The home offers vacant possession...be moved in ready for Christmas
• Huge potential to renovate and add your own style to this amazing property
• 3 Bedrooms Plus 3 Bathrooms
• Master bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite
• Bedroom 2 also has an ensuite
• Open plan design kitchen with stone benchtops
• Separate dining and family rooms opening out to the rear patio. Ideal for a family needing room to move
• Spacious lounge room with high vaulted ceilings
• Loads of room to add that dream pool you have always wanted
• Parklands at the rear of the property, perfect privacy
• Air conditioning throughout
• Double lock up garage
• Walk to Robina Town Centre, Hospital and Train station
• Superb location in the heart of Robina
